snippet.title: Ghost Recon Breakpoint: Welcome To Ghost Recon Delta Company
snippet.description:
Ghost Recon Delta Company is a brand new community program for Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon Breakpoint. 

Community Developers, Laura and Grace, talk you through how the program works and how you could become a Delta Ghost.

If you're passionate about our game and love to express that, then head over to our website to find out more about Ghost Recon Delta Company: ghostrecon.com/DeltaCompany
